1
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:41,220
=The Glory=

2
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:17,060
(Court of Judicial Review)

3
00:02:34,820 --> 00:02:38,660
=Episode 27=

4
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,710
Are you admitting to everything?

5
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:46,920
What if I say

6
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,960
it was Zhuang Shiyang

7
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,880
who secretly framed me?

8
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,040
Mr. Yan,

9
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,640
would you believe that?

10
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,080
Do you have any solid proof?

11
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:58,590
Previously, Zhuang Shiyang
wrote a statement

12
00:02:58,590 --> 00:03:00,270
regarding the case of the adopted son.

13
00:03:00,590 --> 00:03:02,390
I've had it verified by the scribe.

14
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,360
The fingerprints on it
are completely different

15
00:03:05,590 --> 00:03:06,670
from those on the IOUs.

16
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,440
Then I admit it.

17
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:11,650
The day you and Zhuang Hanyan
left the Capital,

18
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:14,080
the Judicial Review received
an anonymous tip,

19
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,280
accusing you

20
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,950
of being Pei's adopted son

21
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:19,880
and of secretly laundering money
for them over the years.

22
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,310
Later,

23
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,550
you even involved Zhuang Hanyan

24
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,870
and committed crimes together.

25
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,370
(Calligraphy and Painting)
I led people to your home

26
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:29,020
and indeed found a large number of IOUs

27
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,670
in your study,

28
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:33,200
totaling over ten million taels
of silver.

29
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:35,600
The debtors were spread
across the country,

30
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,270
and the creditors
were Zhuang Hanyan alone.

31
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:39,920
Now,

32
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,440
it might not be enough for you

33
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,370
to confess to all the crimes.

34
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,080
Have you ever

35
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,510
calculated how old Zhuang Hanyan was

36
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:53,110
at that time based on the loan dates?

37
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:55,750
She was a poor orphan,

38
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,830
raised in a destitute place.

39
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,880
How could she

40
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,390
possibly have so much money?

41
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,400
How could she have the means

42
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,950
to lend the money across the nation?

43
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,390
She's just my scapegoat.

44
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,670
I used her to do everything.

45
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,470
Based on the loan dates,

46
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,150
you and Zhuang Hanyan
were thousands of miles apart,

47
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:21,150
and you weren't even married.

48
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,430
How did you

49
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,710
put this ten million taels of silver

50
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,240
under her name?

51
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,390
I had a marriage contract with her.

52
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,950
Using her name

53
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:33,190
could fool the public.

54
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:34,320
Nonsense.

55
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,070
If you had decided from the beginning

56
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,350
to make her the scapegoat,

57
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,830
why are you now willing
to risk your life

58
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,390
to save hers?

59
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,240
Mr. Yan,

60
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,830
you have a wife and a daughter.

61
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:53,030
Are you really going to pursue this
so relentlessly?

62
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,320
You all may leave.

63
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,400
Yes.

64
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:07,750
Fu Yunxi,

65
00:05:09,290 --> 00:05:10,790
we're alone now.

66
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,270
Tell me honestly.

67
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,120
Did you do this?

68
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:19,060
Mr. Yan, you've always been meticulous

69
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:22,000
in handling cases,

70
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,390
seeing through every detail.

71
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:25,270
Can't you really see

72
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,880
the oddities in this case?

73
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:31,640
The adopted son case
has dragged on for so long

74
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,030
and is unable to be solved.

75
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,640
The Emperor is already dissatisfied.

76
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,430
I've been long investigating it,

77
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:38,320
but I still haven't found
any concrete evidence.

78
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,200
I'm inevitably guilty.

79
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:42,590
Now, with all this forged evidence,

80
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,200
my wife and I are
about to be wrongfully executed.

81
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,270
I can't catch the real culprit,

82
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,190
but I can't let

83
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:51,190
my wife

84
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:52,590
lose her life as well.

85
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,200
Let's put aside the oddities
of this case for now.

86
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,760
Based on our years as colleagues,

87
00:05:59,950 --> 00:06:01,640
I know you well.

88
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,150
You couldn't have

89
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,240
committed such a heinous crime.

90
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:08,830
I...

91
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,240
I have one request.

92
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:13,790
What is it?

93
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:16,150
Now that the money has been found

94
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,510
and I've been caught as a criminal,

95
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,080
this case will be handled well.

96
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,470
The Emperor will certainly be pleased.

97
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,560
Now, let me trade my life

98
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,240
for you to achieve merit and promotion.

99
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,760
For the sake of our years of friendship,

100
00:06:33,430 --> 00:06:34,880
please protect my family.

101
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:36,790
Is that okay?

102
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,920
Fine.

103
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,510
I promise you.

104
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,500
(Creditor: Zhuang Hanyan)

105
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:23,500
(Creditor: Zhuang Hanyan)

106
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:26,190
My Lord,

107
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,400
Zhuang Hanyan is here.

108
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,050
- Let her in.
- Yes.

109
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:35,340
(Justice Without Mercy)

110
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:37,440
Greetings, Mr. Yan. I...

111
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,100
Mrs. Fu, please don't stand on ceremony.

112
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:41,560
Please press your fingerprints first

113
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:43,200
before we discuss other matters.

114
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:07,560
My Lord,

115
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,920
the fingerprints on this IOU

116
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,830
aren't the same as Zhuang Hanyan's.

117
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,160
This case

118
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,390
was indeed all done by Fu Yunxi alone.

119
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,190
You may leave.

120
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,720
- Yes.
- Yes.

121
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,310
Mr. Yan, Fu Yunxi...

122
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:27,550
Fu Yunxi has taken full responsibility
for everything.

123
00:08:27,630 --> 00:08:30,200
With the evidence I currently have,

124
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:31,610
I can't prove any direct connection

125
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:33,300
between you and this case.

126
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:34,830
For now, you may leave.

127
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,880
Later,

128
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,880
if the Three Judicial Offices
investigate again,

129
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,200
just claim you know nothing,

130
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,470
and you'll be fine.

131
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:41,830
Mr. Yan,

132
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,440
this case is indeed related to me,

133
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,590
and I know the truth.

134
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,630
Fu Yunxi is innocent.

135
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:50,160
Please let me meet him.

136
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,280
Now, he's determined to die.

137
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:53,560
Even if you go,

138
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,240
he won't meet you.

139
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,160
It's impossible.

140
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,590
He's not someone
who would easily seek death.

141
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:02,620
Moreover, he has a widowed mother
and a young daughter.

142
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:05,280
How could he willingly die like this?

143
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,680
Even if he's willing to die,

144
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,600
why won't he meet me?

145
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,200
This case is highly complex.

146
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,400
It's already a great fortune

147
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,750
for him to clear you.

148
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,400
Don't waste any more time.

149
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,320
Mrs. Fu, please leave.

150
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,440
My Lord,

151
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:24,670
Fu Yunxi's barely breathing.

152
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,630
He has fainted again.

153
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:27,960
Summon the physician.

154
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:28,810
Yes.

155
00:09:28,830 --> 00:09:29,710
Mr. Yan.

156
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:30,550
(Quiet Wave)

157
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,470
Mr. Yan.

158
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,950
Mrs. Fu, please don't act rashly.

159
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,870
We can think of a way back at home.

160
00:09:35,870 --> 00:09:36,840
Mr. Yan,

161
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,550
Fu Yunxi is not Pei's adopted son

162
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:40,430
but has infiltrated
the Pei faction as a spy.

163
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:45,280
The former Chief Minister,
Wen Mingchang,

164
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,120
ordered Fu Yunxi

165
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,650
to infiltrate the Pei faction as a spy.

166
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:49,790
Over the years,

167
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:53,040
Fu Yunxi has indeed been
involved with the Pei faction,

168
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,120
but his goal was to eliminate

169
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,140
these treacherous eunuchs.

170
00:09:56,310 --> 00:09:57,480
Do you have any evidence

171
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,830
of what you say?

172
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:01,920
I don't have evidence,

173
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:04,040
and neither does Fu Yunxi.

174
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,840
But I still ask you

175
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,230
to report this to the Emperor

176
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,590
and seek the Emperor's judgment

177
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:10,830
to grant Fu Yunxi

178
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,320
a chance to live.

179
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:14,480
You must not speak recklessly

180
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,710
just to save your husband.

181
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,830
What I've said isn't a lie.

182
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,040
No.

183
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,350
You have no proof.

184
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,080
If we rashly go to the Palace,

185
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,520
the risks are immense.

186
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,750
Fu Yunxi certainly knows
the gravity of this,

187
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:32,560
or he would've told me long ago.

188
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,150
If there's anyone to be blamed,

189
00:10:36,150 --> 00:10:37,540
I'll take the blame for everything.

190
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:38,550
Mr. Yan,

191
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,910
please allow me to meet Fu Yunxi.

192
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:42,320
Send Mrs. Fu home.

193
00:10:43,510 --> 00:10:44,430
Mr. Yan.

194
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:45,590
Mr. Yan.

195
00:10:50,060 --> 00:10:55,260
(Light, Fu Residence)

196
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,920
Madam.

197
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:26,080
Madam, you're finally back.

198
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,400
Yunxi.

199
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,760
Hanyan.

200
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,360
Hanyan.

201
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,830
Where's Yunxi?

202
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,560
Why hasn't he come back?

203
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,830
He's still
in the Judicial Review, right?

204
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,590
Didn't you go

205
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:41,450
on a spring outing to the outskirts?

206
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,750
How could he end up becoming

207
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:43,870
Eunuch Pei's adopted son

208
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:45,280
after this journey?

209
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,240
Mother,

210
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:49,080
Grandmother said
you went to fetch Father,

211
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,950
but why didn't Father return with you?

212
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,760
Lingzhi, my dear.

213
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,080
Your father went to work.

214
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,950
He'll return once he finishes it.

215
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,670
Hanyan,

216
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,120
is it right?

217
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,880
Yunxi

218
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:06,590
is still alive, right?

219
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,760
Mother,

220
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,440
sorry for my incompetence.

221
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:19,670
Yunxi

222
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:23,400
is trapped in the prison

223
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,520
and is determined to die.

224
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,040
He doesn't want to see me.

225
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,920
Ma'am...

226
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:33,830
Hanyan.

227
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,830
Madam.

228
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,480
It's all my fault.

229
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,470
- Aunt Kou.
- I'm useless.

230
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,990
I used to make things hard for you.

231
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,320
I'm sorry. I'll kowtow to you.

232
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,200
Aunt Kou.

233
00:12:45,210 --> 00:12:46,060
Aunt Kou, please rise.

234
00:12:46,070 --> 00:12:47,630
- I apologize.
- Please get up.

235
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:50,280
- Get up.
- Save Yunxi.

236
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,590
- Aunt Kou.
- Hanyan,

237
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:57,150
I know you are more capable than I am.

238
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:59,270
You know many noble ladies.

239
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:01,320
You must have a way to save Yunxi,

240
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,240
right?

241
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:04,440
The entire family

242
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:07,350
is depending on you, Madam.

243
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:08,750
I promise you.

244
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,280
Once you save Yunxi,

245
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,470
I will leave.

246
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:14,080
I'll return to my hometown;
I won't bother you anymore.

247
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,120
- Aunt Kou.
- I beg you.

248
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,470
Aunt Kou, Aunt Kou.

249
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,080
Fu Yunxi is my husband.

250
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,280
I'll think of every possible way
to bring him back.

251
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,630
- Really?
- Really?

252
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:26,590
Mother,

253
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,520
Aunt Kou,

254
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,040
Lingzhi,

255
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:38,400
I swear here

256
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,200
that I will bring

257
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,000
Fu Yunxi back.

258
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,160
Hanyan.

259
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,840
- Madam.
- Madam.

260
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,760
Where are we going?

261
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,150
Let's go to the Deng Mansion first.

262
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:05,420
(Deng Mansion)
Open the door.

263
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,630
Is anyone there?

264
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,400
It's Zhuang Hanyan.

265
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,560
Open up.

266
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:10,990
Mr. Deng.

267
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,760
Mr. Deng.

268
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:25,820
(Yu Pavilion, Yao Residence)

269
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:37,420
(Currency)

270
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,710
Mr. Li.

271
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:47,780
(Li Mansion)
Mr. Li.

272
00:14:50,270 --> 00:14:51,190
Move.

273
00:14:56,340 --> 00:15:01,260
(Duke Qi's Mansion)

274
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:02,240
Madam,

275
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,360
we're at Duke Qi's Mansion.

276
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:09,160
Madam,

277
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,160
you'd better not visit.

278
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:32,260
(Zhuiyue Pavilion)

279
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:34,520
Greetings, Your Highness.
I'm Zhuang Hanyan.

280
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,280
I heard that you know the art of tea.

281
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:46,280
As your elder sister,

282
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:48,630
I wonder if you mind
brewing a pot for me.

283
00:15:50,510 --> 00:15:51,560
Yushan, you're too polite.

284
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:53,680
I wouldn't dare to refuse.

285
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:06,320
You don't think
I still have lingering feelings

286
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,630
for Fu Yunxi, do you?

287
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,680
I only ask you

288
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,440
to kindly pass a message

289
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:15,440
so that I may meet Duke Qi.

290
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,080
What will you do after that?

291
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,970
I only want to resolve
past misunderstandings.

292
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,230
He doesn't have to save him.

293
00:16:21,830 --> 00:16:24,350
I just want him to pull some strings
with the Judicial Review

294
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:26,200
and let me meet Fu Yunxi.

295
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,280
Yushan, please have some tea.

296
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,660
Your Highness, please have some tea.

297
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,430
What if

298
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,350
I refuse?

299
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:17,190
Yushan,

300
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,350
your mother

301
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,000
was almost killed by Zhuang Shiyang.

302
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,560
Fu Yunxi and I saved her.

303
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,270
- What?
- Don't worry.

304
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:28,910
We've sheltered her.

305
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:32,040
Zhuang Shiyang is no good.

306
00:17:32,350 --> 00:17:33,880
Over the years, you and your mother

307
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:35,320
have been deeply deceived by him.

308
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:38,190
Your mother has finally woken up.

309
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,280
Are you still going to be
the foolish daughter

310
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:44,040
of Pei's adopted son?

311
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:46,920
Zhuang Hanyan,

312
00:17:47,830 --> 00:17:49,070
stop spouting nonsense

313
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,040
and twisting the truth.

314
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,350
I know better than you

315
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:54,110
what a man Father is

316
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:56,070
after all these years in the family.

317
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,120
Besides,

318
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,870
no one is willing to help you now.

319
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,720
Without a man,

320
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,280
you are nothing.

321
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:05,710
Let her go.

322
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:19,780
(Zhuiyue Pavilion)

323
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:56,680
(I don't have the ability to protect
your family as you expect.)

324
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,600
(Perhaps)

325
00:18:58,240 --> 00:19:00,430
(you chose the wrong woman
from the start.)

326
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,870
Hanyan.

327
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:25,600
You...

328
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,390
Why...?

329
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,040
Hanyan,

330
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,590
I finally found you.

331
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,880
We...

332
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:34,830
We are here to help you.

333
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:40,810
You once helped me before,

334
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,110
but I couldn't disobey my father,

335
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:43,350
so I was late.

336
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,280
Please don't blame me.

337
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:48,350
Though we're just acquaintances,

338
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:50,760
just consider me here for the fun of it.

339
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,670
Thank you.

340
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,080
Thank you.

341
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:01,210
Someone in the Judicial Review said

342
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:03,160
that Fu Yunxi may have been ordered

343
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,450
to be a spy in the Pei faction.

344
00:20:04,690 --> 00:20:06,620
Didn't this leave any evidence?

345
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,400
Time has passed;

346
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,480
evidence is hard to find.

347
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,430
But if I could meet Fu Yunxi

348
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:15,080
and get more info,

349
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:17,830
perhaps we could find more evidence.

350
00:20:18,270 --> 00:20:20,080
Unfortunately,
the prison is heavily guarded,

351
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:22,310
and Mr. Yan won't even let me

352
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:24,000
step inside the Judicial Review.

353
00:20:24,350 --> 00:20:25,480
I have a cousin

354
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:27,110
who was imprisoned
last year for a fight.

355
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,910
Perhaps you could use my name

356
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,640
to visit him in prison.

357
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,680
That would be great.

358
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:33,480
I'll send someone
to bribe the prison guards

359
00:20:33,820 --> 00:20:35,310
and arrange for you

360
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:36,960
to meet Fu Yunxi after you enter.

361
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,040
This is a major case.

362
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,910
Any misstep could lead to trouble.

363
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:43,830
Are you really

364
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,230
going to help me?

365
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:48,630
Duke Qi holds immense power.

366
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,430
If you hadn't helped me back then,

367
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,830
I might have

368
00:20:53,070 --> 00:20:54,590
already died.

369
00:20:55,310 --> 00:20:56,830
Now that you're in trouble,

370
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,590
how could I just stand by and watch?

371
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:01,430
Throughout history, men's friendships
have always been praised.

372
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,160
Why can't I be warm-hearted

373
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,540
and ready to help today?

374
00:21:04,540 --> 00:21:05,930
Women's friendship is also valuable.

375
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:06,830
I'm determined

376
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,240
to help you.

377
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:09,830
I am incompetent and foolish,

378
00:21:10,110 --> 00:21:11,030
so all I can do

379
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,520
is pray

380
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:14,960
for all of you.

381
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:20,590
Please

382
00:21:21,830 --> 00:21:23,430
accept my gratitude here.

383
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,800
- Hanyan.
- Please rise.

384
00:21:37,220 --> 00:21:41,620
(Court of Judicial Review)

385
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,590
Who are you?

386
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:45,630
I'm Yao Wangshu, daughter
of Yao Zhidong, Grand Secretary.

387
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:46,950
I'm here to visit a prisoner.

388
00:21:48,180 --> 00:21:49,500
(One member is allowed to visit)

389
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,430
Pass.

390
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:05,500
(Court of Judicial Review)

391
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,030
Behave yourself.

392
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:08,550
I'm innocent.

393
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:11,520
You have only
half an incense stick of time.

394
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,320
Thank you, sir.

395
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,920
It's fine.

396
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:28,840
Fu Yunxi.

397
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,120
Fu Yunxi.

398
