00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:44,910
Fu Yunxi.

401
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:51,110
You've confessed.

402
00:22:53,030 --> 00:22:55,520
Why are you still tortured?

403
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:59,320
You shouldn't be here.

404
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,390
Go back.

405
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,190
I'll return,

406
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:06,960
and I'll bring you back

407
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,830
safe and sound.

408
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:14,800
Don't worry.

409
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:17,560
I've tried to pull some strings outside.

410
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,960
The powerful and noble in the Capital

411
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,760
are willing to help.

412
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:24,190
Your name will soon be cleared.

413
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,150
You must not give up.

414
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:32,480
No one knows you better than I do

415
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:34,720
when you lie.

416
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:39,720
Stop trying to save me.

417
00:23:41,030 --> 00:23:42,520
Take care of yourself,

418
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,910
and take care of our family.

419
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:47,760
As long as you are safe and happy,

420
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:50,520
I will be content.

421
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,630
Though this is extremely hard,

422
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,870
it is not entirely without hope.

423
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,760
You aren't someone
who'd easily give up on your life.

424
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,350
What are you truly afraid of?

425
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,590
If you fear dragging me down,

426
00:24:08,110 --> 00:24:09,240
you are wrong.

427
00:24:10,310 --> 00:24:12,830
I do not want this kind
of self-righteous care for me.

428
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,590
Mother cared for me,

429
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:20,040
cutting off our ties for 17 years.

430
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,140
But she didn't know

431
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:24,360
that I'd rather be trapped
in Zhuang Residence with her

432
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:26,190
than be a child without a mother.

433
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:28,720
Chai Jing cared for me,

434
00:24:29,260 --> 00:24:31,790
so she took the blame and went
to prison for me behind my back.

435
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:32,960
But she didn't know

436
00:24:35,110 --> 00:24:37,720
that watching her never being able
to hold a saber again

437
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,960
was more painful
than if I had been killed.

438
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,350
Fu Yunxi,

439
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:45,040
do you want me

440
00:24:45,790 --> 00:24:48,430
to endure this kind of pain again?

441
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:50,670
Zhuang Hanyan,

442
00:24:53,310 --> 00:24:55,280
I am a despicable man,

443
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:56,830
unworthy

444
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:59,720
of your sincere feelings

445
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:02,240
and honest treatment.

446
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,040
You do have another secret.

447
00:25:06,350 --> 00:25:07,830
I have long been poisoned,

448
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,350
and my life is nearly over.

449
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,110
You want to find a woman with the means

450
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:14,980
to protect your family

451
00:25:15,050 --> 00:25:16,830
and you to secretly keep
the enormous fortune

452
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:18,110
of the Zuohang Gang...

453
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:19,520
Did something go wrong?

454
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,670
Poisoned?

455
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,720
It was five years ago.

456
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:36,240
On the day Yuqin was poisoned,

457
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,240
I also drank half a cup

458
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:40,630
of the poisoned wine on the table.

459
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,520
Yunxi.

460
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:47,110
Yunxi, Yunxi.

461
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,320
Yunxi, Yunxi.

462
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,640
What's wrong?

463
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,200
- Are you okay, Yunxi?
- Are you okay?

464
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,870
- Yunxi, open the door.
- Yunxi.

465
00:25:53,950 --> 00:25:55,150
- I'm fine.
- Open the door.

466
00:25:55,350 --> 00:25:56,270
I'm fine.

467
00:25:58,110 --> 00:26:00,110
The poison is complex,

468
00:26:00,790 --> 00:26:01,870
and it can't be cured.

469
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:05,720
I can only use rare herbs
to prolong my life,

470
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:08,720
but I don't know
how much longer I can last.

471
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,560
I've made too many enemies
because of my job.

472
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:14,910
If I die,

473
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:18,630
my entire family will be revenged.

474
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,960
That's why I decided

475
00:26:22,550 --> 00:26:24,550
to find a strategist to protect

476
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:25,870
my family as my wife,

477
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,830
and you appeared

478
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:34,960
in my sight at that moment.

479
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:38,350
The day we met,

480
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,960
I knew in my heart

481
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,960
you were the one I was looking for.

482
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:46,080
I knew my time was short,

483
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,070
and I dared not fall in love,

484
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:50,000
nor could I stir your feelings.

485
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:55,280
But I underestimated you.

486
00:26:56,270 --> 00:26:57,910
The more I restrained myself,

487
00:26:58,070 --> 00:27:00,080
the harder it became to control myself.

488
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:03,080
I kept having improper thoughts
about you.

489
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,670
Your occasional tenderness in return

490
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:09,320
made me happy

491
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:12,590
but also guilty and regretful.

492
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,390
Perhaps

493
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:18,110
from the very first day we met,

494
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:21,590
I thought I was the one hunting the fox,

495
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,760
(Happiness)
but I'd been captured by you.

496
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,630
Later,

497
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:32,280
our marriage, protection, and alliances

498
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,430
were just excuses

499
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,240
to deceive you

500
