and deceive me.

501
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:40,670
Now,

502
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:43,080
with my dying body,

503
00:27:43,590 --> 00:27:45,150
I'll take on all the blame,

504
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:47,110
and everything will be resolved.

505
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:50,630
