on investigating the adopted son

507
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:55,390
because of that enormous fortune.

508
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:58,320
Now, I'll take all the blame,

509
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,630
and Mr. Yan will protect

510
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,960
my family from being implicated.

511
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,080
There's one more thing.

512
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:09,720
When I first went to Danzhou,

513
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:12,070
I found a large sum of money

514
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:14,830
Zhuang Shiyang had not yet moved.

515
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,110
The amount is considerable.

516
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,280
It's hidden in our secret compartment.

517
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,600
It can ensure that you

518
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:24,590
will no longer suffer

519
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:26,520
for the rest of your life.

520
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,910
Stop trying to save me.

521
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:36,110
Take this money

522
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:38,560
and our family

523
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,720
and leave for another place.

524
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:49,040
Fu Yunxi,

525
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:52,040
I've long known
that you had other plans,

526
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:56,110
and I've realized
you were hiding something.

527
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,430
But I didn't know you could be so cruel.

528
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,720
You deceived me

529
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,830
