♪In my winter sky♪

566
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,830
It's true that I harmed you in the past,

567
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,430
but this time,

568
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:39,430
I truly want to help you.

569
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,760
Yet in the end,

570
00:31:41,310 --> 00:31:42,430
I still messed it up.

571
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:44,320
Ms. Zhou,

572
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:49,630
have you ever longed
for a lifetime of happiness

573
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,110
with your beloved?

574
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:56,040
Falling in love

575
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,110
and exchanging true feelings

576
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:01,150
are a luxury to me.

577
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:04,390
I only want to live well.

578
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:07,350
Fu Yunxi once asked me this question,

579
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:11,870
and I answered in the same way.

580
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,320
What about now?

581
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:17,520
When it comes to love,

582
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,480
only those who have had it

583
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,720
and who have felt it

584
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,870
can know how precious it is,

585
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:27,190
and only then do they know

586
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:29,590
how terrifying it is.

587
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:32,630
It can make you lose your sense

588
00:32:33,550 --> 00:32:35,390
and uncontrollably want more.

589
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,080
I once thought

590
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:41,870
love was not important to me,

591
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:45,280
but now, looking back,

592
00:32:47,830 --> 00:32:49,670
all the schemes and tests

593
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:51,390
I had with him

594
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,910
were because

595
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:59,080
I had already fallen for him.

596
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:02,080
You still want to save him?

597
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:07,280
My mother and I

598
00:33:09,750 --> 00:33:11,390
only had a hundred days together.

599
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,720
After she passed, I realized

600
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:17,350
how precious every day

601
00:33:19,310 --> 00:33:20,560
I spent with her had been.

602
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:23,350
Such is the way of the world
and of human hearts.

603
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:27,190
Only after losing something

604
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,830
do you realize its value.

605
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,240
Only after losing it

606
00:33:34,070 --> 00:33:35,240
do you regret it.

607
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,040
But this time,

608
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,000
I don't want to repeat that.

609
00:33:46,110 --> 00:33:48,240
I've said something out of anger today,

610
00:33:49,590 --> 00:33:51,390
but how could I abandon him?

611
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:54,560
How could I watch him
die unjustly in prison?

612
00:33:57,030 --> 00:33:58,240
So, what are you

613
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,390
going to do next?

614
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,960
Now, to save him,

615
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:03,670
I must prove that he was ordered

616
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,320
to be a spy in the Pei faction.

617
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,040
Though there is no evidence,

618
00:34:07,410 --> 00:34:09,670
I am the only one

619
00:34:10,000 --> 00:34:11,880
who knows the truth.

620
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,000
I can be his witness.

621
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,510
However,

622
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,920
you are his wife.

623
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,590
How can such a testimony

624
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,190
be trusted by the Judicial Review?

625
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:25,020
The Appeal Drum is
just outside the Palace.

626
00:34:25,150 --> 00:34:26,440
As long as I beat it,

627
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,710
I can enter the Palace

628
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:29,720
and present my plea before the Emperor.

629
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,590
How confident are you?

630
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:34,710
It doesn't matter.

631
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:38,480
This is the only path I have left.

632
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:40,710
I must try

633
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,960
everything in my power

634
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:44,590
and do whatever I can.

635
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:47,080
Even if it ends in failure,

636
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:49,440
and he still has to die,

637
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:51,230
at least

638
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,230
I can face Lingzhi in the future.

639
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:58,080
At least in my midnight dreams,

640
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:01,190
I won't regret and feel uneasy.

641
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:04,360
Do you think I'm foolish?

642
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:08,070
I actually envy you a little

643
00:35:08,070 --> 00:35:09,480
for having encountered someone

644
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:12,320
who makes you take risks

645
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,710
and disregard everything.

646
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:19,280
Madam.

647
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,520
Who is this lady?

648
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,840
She's Mrs. Wen who went
to the house to see you,

649
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:29,230
so I brought her here.

650
00:35:29,790 --> 00:35:31,880
I am the widow of Wen Mingchang.

651
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,040
Are you

652
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:37,200
Mrs. Wen?

653
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:39,320
Yes.

654
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,240
Mrs. Wen,

655
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,360
I once went

656
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:44,880
to search for Mr. Wen's family,

657
00:35:45,400 --> 00:35:47,060
but I was told that after his passing,

658
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,750
his family moved away
from their old home,

659
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:50,230
and no one knows their whereabouts.

660
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:54,310
Do you know anything

661
00:35:55,110 --> 00:35:57,000
about Fu Yunxi's being a spy
in the Pei faction?

662
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:58,510
Mrs. Fu,

663
00:35:58,510 --> 00:35:59,880
if you enter the Palace

664
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:01,270
to meet the Emperor with this,

665
00:36:01,510 --> 00:36:03,630
you'll be more likely to succeed.

666
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,230
What's this?

667
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:07,920
I heard you broke
into the Judicial Review

668
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,270
to save your husband,

669
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:12,280
claiming that Fu Yunxi was ordered
by my husband, Wen Mingchang

670
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:14,960
to be a spy in the Pei faction.

671
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,110
When I heard this,

672
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:19,110
I was relieved,

673
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,310
so I came to visit.

674
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:24,110
Please open this letter

675
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,270
and learn the truth.

676
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:35,960
The Pei faction is cruel,
persecuting those who oppose them.

677
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:38,670
Eunuch Pei may have suspected
my disloyalty.

678
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:41,350
Recently, I have been secretly followed,

679
00:36:41,550 --> 00:36:43,590
and there have been attempts on my life.

680
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:47,670
You've managed to infiltrate the faction
and gained that eunuch's trust.

681
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:49,520
It must've been hard.

682
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:53,670
I hope one day to cleanse the court
and restore order.

683
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:56,630
I have written down
the details in a secret code

684
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:59,840
and hidden it in a memorial
for the Emperor.

685
00:37:00,030 --> 00:37:01,880
- If something happens to me,
- Search.

686
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:03,630
- you can use this memorial
- Hurry.

687
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:06,150
- to prove your innocence.
- Guards!

688
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:07,200
There's an assassin!

689
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:09,590
Search every room.

690
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:10,510
Yes.

691
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,320
Hurry.

692
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,840
Search carefully.

693
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:19,920
Catch the assassin!

694
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,840
Madam, Mr. Wen is in the study.

695
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:39,280
Master.

696
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:41,070
Master.

697
00:37:42,190 --> 00:37:44,480
Master.

698
00:37:45,110 --> 00:37:46,670
Master, what's wrong?

699
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,710
Master.

700
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,550
What do you want?

701
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,480
Deliver the letter.

702
00:37:54,080 --> 00:37:55,630
Since there is Mr. Wen's secret letter,

703
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:57,000
why not present it to the Palace

704
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,190
and let the Emperor decide?

705
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:00,400
Mr. Wen has passed away.

706
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:02,190
What if someone is framing him,

707
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,590
claiming that this letter is forged?

708
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:07,560
Could it result in the crime
of deceiving the Emperor?

709
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:10,270
This letter is not the key.

710
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,280
What can truly

711
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,270
save Fu Yunxi

712
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,880
is this.

713
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:16,030
(Memorial)

714
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:16,950
That's right.

715
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,470
Earlier,

716
00:38:19,230 --> 00:38:20,630
I was so delighted

717
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:22,920
because I saw hope in this.

718
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,480
Imperial memorials

719
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:25,750
are always kept in the Palace.

720
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:28,560
It seems that we must first report it
to the Emperor.

721
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:31,160
But I'm afraid that if we hastily
present it to the Palace,

722
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:33,270
and this memorial can't be found,

723
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:35,620
we will be left with no way
to defend ourselves

724
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:37,550
and still be accused
of deceiving the Emperor.

725
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:39,520
I once heard Zhuang Shiyang mention

726
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:42,320
that copies of imperial memorials

727
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:44,000
are stored in the Office
of Transmission.

728
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,670
The Transmission?

729
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,830
The current Principal Graduate,

730
00:38:47,830 --> 00:38:49,970
He Wenshen, was assigned
to the Transmission, right?

731
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:53,000
It's him.

732
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:54,920
I remember at the Lantern Festival,

733
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,840
he seemed to favor you.

734
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:58,230
His proposal

735
00:38:58,230 --> 00:38:59,520
ended up awkward.

736
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:02,360
If he still harbors resentment

737
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,150
and learns of this secret,

738
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,400
he may

739
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,880
ruin the copy of the memorial first.

740
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:10,670
You only have

741
00:39:10,890 --> 00:39:13,480
to ask him to let you
into the Transmission.

742
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,400
But we have to consider

743
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,360
whether he would be willing to meet me

744
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,310
and listen to my plea.

745
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,840
I have a way.

746
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:24,770
Mr. He once studied
at the Directorate of Education.

747
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,710
My grandfather taught him
for a few days.

748
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,710
Maybe he will help me because of it.

749
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,700
(Office of Transmission)

750
00:39:37,550 --> 00:39:38,240
Mr. He,

751
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:40,960
this letter was sent from Mr. Deng
of the Directorate of Education.

752
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:46,940
(To Wenshen: I'll wait for you
at Hongyun Hall at the Xu hour.)

753
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:49,080
Mr. Deng?

754
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,800
Zhuang Hanyan.

755
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,680
Mr. He.

756
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,680
Why is it you?

757
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:12,270
Mr. He, forgive me.

758
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:13,960
I used

759
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,880
Mr. Deng's name

760
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:16,920
to meet with you.

761
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:18,470
Mr. He,

762
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:20,150
please have some tea.

763
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:27,750
You really are bold

764
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:29,880
to impersonate an official.

765
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,960
I am grateful for your favor

766
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:38,590
and for proposing to me
at Zhuang Residence.

767
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:39,960
Yet, it didn't end pleasantly,

768
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,840
which has left me uneasy.

769
00:40:43,190 --> 00:40:45,110
Today, I have set a modest banquet

770
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:47,440
to seek your forgiveness.

771
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,880
Don't beat around the bush.

772
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,920
Now, Fu Yunxi is imprisoned.

773
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,760
Do you want me to save him?

774
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,320
Mr. He, you're a wise and honorable man.

775
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,590
I dare not hide it from you.

776
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,070
Today, to save my husband,

777
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:03,310
there is a request I must make.

778
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:05,590
What request?

779
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:07,000
I want to enter the Transmission

780
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:08,840
to find a copy of the memorial.

781
00:41:09,110 --> 00:41:10,030
What?

782
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:11,920
I am not yet able to reveal

783
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,270
the details of this,

784
00:41:14,030 --> 00:41:15,440
but I beg you to grant my request.

785
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:20,960
You refused my proposal before.

786
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:23,000
Have you ever thought it'd come to this?

787
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,480
It's my fault

788
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,140
for failing to see your potential.

789
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,360
We haven't met for so long.

790
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:35,840
Now, I'm an official,
while you're just a common woman.

791
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:38,400
But you didn't kneel and kowtow to me,

792
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,920
calling me "My Lord".

793
00:41:45,070 --> 00:41:46,110
If there's nothing else,

794
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:47,360
I must take my leave.

795
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,510
My Lord, I'm Zhuang Hanyan.

796
00:41:48,510 --> 00:41:49,840
I beg you for mercy.

797
00:42:00,070 --> 00:42:02,560
You truly are a devoted woman.

798
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:04,800
Fine.

799
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:07,560
Come to the Transmission tomorrow night.

800
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:09,840
I will send someone to meet you.

801
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:11,960
Thank you, Mr. He.

802
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:28,040
What memorial copy do you need?

803
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:30,630
The memorials
from the Judicial Review last year.

804
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:33,030
They're all here.

805
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:35,200
There are date labels
on the bookshelves.

806
00:42:35,670 --> 00:42:36,590
You can search slowly.

807
00:42:37,030 --> 00:42:38,080
Be careful with the fire.

808
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:39,920
Thank you, Mr. He.

809
00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:05,800
(Wen Mingchang, Chief Minister,
Month 3, Day 15, Year 3)

810
00:43:18,350 --> 00:43:19,870
There's light at the central archives.

811
00:43:19,960 --> 00:43:21,310
As expected, a thief has broken in.

812
00:43:37,300 --> 00:43:38,420
(Respectfully, Wen Mingchang)

813
00:44:05,550 --> 00:44:06,470
Where is the thief?

814
00:44:07,590 --> 00:44:08,790
My Lord, the window.

815
00:44:15,320 --> 00:44:16,550
Backyard. Chase her.

816
00:44:16,550 --> 00:44:17,470
Yes.

817
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:41,240
- Madam.
- Madam.

818
00:44:42,230 --> 00:44:44,110
The thief is here. Capture her.

819
00:44:44,110 --> 00:44:46,780
(Office of Transmission)

820
00:44:50,590 --> 00:44:51,960
Shameless thief.

821
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:53,750
How dare you break into the Transmission

822
00:44:54,110 --> 00:44:55,480
and steal imperial memorials!

823
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:56,680
Seize her.

824
00:44:59,590 --> 00:45:00,510
Stop.

825
00:45:15,590 --> 00:45:18,480
I'm the granddaughter of Mr. Deng,
Chancellor of the Education.

826
00:45:18,480 --> 00:45:20,110
Let me see who dares to touch me.

827
00:45:20,950 --> 00:45:23,540
I'm the daughter of Mr. Yao,
Grand Secretary of the Secretariat.

828
00:45:23,590 --> 00:45:24,870
Who is the shameless thief here?

829
00:45:25,590 --> 00:45:28,000
I'm the daughter of Mr. Li,
Grand Councilor of the Right.

830
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:29,270
Retreat now.

831
00:45:29,800 --> 00:45:31,760
How dare you protect the thief?

832
00:45:31,760 --> 00:45:33,460
Don't you fear
the Three Judicial Offices?

833
00:45:33,550 --> 00:45:35,310
The Reviewer
of the Judicial Review is here.

834
00:45:36,190 --> 00:45:37,760
I'll ask you first about your crimes.

835
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:39,150
Mr. He, you let

836
00:45:39,150 --> 00:45:40,920
a thief into the Transmission

837
00:45:41,150 --> 00:45:42,560
and asked everyone to catch her.

838
00:45:42,920 --> 00:45:44,190
What are you up to?

839
00:45:52,670 --> 00:45:53,590
Kill them.

840
00:45:55,020 --> 00:45:55,880
Protect them.

841
00:45:55,880 --> 00:45:56,800
- Hanyan.
- Hanyan.

842
00:45:57,510 --> 00:45:59,150
Everyone, you...

843
00:45:59,150 --> 00:46:00,960
Don't worry about us. Hurry and leave.

